{{monster info|tengu}}

==Useful Info==
'''Tengu''' are unremarkable flying monsters. Like most monstrous version of the [[tengu|playable species]], they are only as dangerous as the gear they wield. They do not generate naturally, only appearing if a [[shapeshifter (monster)|shapeshifter]] happens to take one's appearance or if you happen to [[polymorph]] a creature and get lucky.

==Tips & Tricks==
Tengu are weak enough to only pose a threat to low-level casters they catch in melee.

==History==
Prior to 0.14, generic tengu used to occasionally show up alongside more dangerous [[list of tengu|tengu]] opponents.
